data.description: Beautifully appointed townhome with CENTRAL AIR CONDITIONING. Look no further, this townhome is the one. Newer appliances and granite countertops make the kitchen inviting. You will appreciate the easy access to the outdoors (adjacent to open space, numerous walking, hiking and mountain biking trails). This is a fantastic 2 bedroom and 3 bathroom townhome, it is an end unit as part of a duplex building. The two car garage is attached, including extra storage or workspace. New paint throughout and new carpeting. Newer roof and gutters, newer furnace, air conditioning unit and hot water heater. Washer and dryer are included. Both bedrooms are located on the upper level, each with its own walk-in closet and attached bathroom. The main level living room has a gas fireplace. Enjoy the semi-enclosed main level outdoor space. Across from Colorado Springs Country Club.
